## Anthropic Messages API Request

```typescript
type AnthropicRequest = {
  model: string;                          // "claude-opus-4-6", "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001"
  messages: Message[];
  system: SystemBlock[];
  tools: Tool[];
  metadata: { user_id: string };
  max_tokens: number;                     // 32000
  temperature: number;                    // 1
  output_config: {
    format: {
      type: "json_schema";
      schema: object;                     // JSON Schema for structured output
    };
  };
  stream: boolean;
};

type Message = {
  role: "user" | "assistant";
  content: string | ContentBlock[];
};

type ContentBlock = { type: "text"; text: string };

type SystemBlock = {
  type: "text";
  text: string;
  cache_control?: { type: "ephemeral" };  // prompt caching
};

type Tool = {
  name: string;                           // "Bash", "Read", "Edit", "Grep", etc.
  description: string;
  input_schema: object;                   // JSON Schema
};
```

## Stream Response (extracted from SSE events)

```typescript
// message_start event → input tokens, model
// message_delta event → output tokens, stop_reason

type StreamSummary = {
  model: string;         // can differ from request (e.g. request="haiku", response resolves to actual model ID)
